WEBVTT

00:00:01.272 --> 00:00:02.649
Zamislite ovo:

00:00:02.649 --> 00:00:03.772
ponedjeljak je.

00:00:03.772 --> 00:00:04.861
Vi ste u uredu.

00:00:04.861 --> 00:00:06.615
Pripremate se za radni dan

00:00:06.615 --> 00:00:09.437
i kolega kojeg poznajete

00:00:09.437 --> 00:00:11.273
dolazi do vašeg stola

00:00:11.273 --> 00:00:12.675
i krade vam stolicu.

00:00:12.675 --> 00:00:13.917
Ne kaže vam ni riječi -

00:00:13.917 --> 00:00:15.305
samo ode s njom.

00:00:15.305 --> 00:00:17.788
Ne kaže vam razlog zbog čega je uzeo
baš vašu stolicu

00:00:17.788 --> 00:00:19.899
od toliko drugih.

00:00:19.899 --> 00:00:22.041
Nije ga briga da li vi trebate stolicu

00:00:22.041 --> 00:00:23.582
da obavite današnji posao.

00:00:23.582 --> 00:00:25.839
Vi to ne bi trpjeli, nego bi napravili
frku.

00:00:25.839 --> 00:00:27.866
Pratili biste tog kolegu do njegovog stola

00:00:27.866 --> 00:00:31.178
i upitali ga "Zašto moja stolica?".